{"lemma":"مَصَّةٍ","slug":"مَصَّةٍ","root":"م.ص.ص","root_slug":"م-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/م-ص-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n38621","n38624"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to suck, to sip up"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of مَصَّ (maṣṣa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sucking, suction, sipping up"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root م ص ص (m ṣ ṣ). Cognate with Hebrew מָצַץ (matsáts)."},"ipa":["/masˤ.sˤa/","/masˤsˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n38621","headword_ar":"مَصَّهُ","root":"mS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSiSotu","text_ar":"مَصِصْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yamaS~u","text_ar":"يَمَصُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) and first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaSotu","text_ar":"مَصَصْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yamuS~u","text_ar":"يَمُصُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K;) but the former is the more chaste; (T, Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maS~N","text_ar":"مَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sucked it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sucked it in;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sipped it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he drank it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(namely water, A, or a thing, S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a minute draught,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$urobFA raqiyqFA","text_ar":"شُرْبًا رَقِيقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": so in a copy of the A, and in the CK,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a gentle draught:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$urobFA rafiyqFA","text_ar":"شُرْبًا رَفِيقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": so in some copies of the K, and in the TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(namely a small quantity of a fluid)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by drawing in the breath:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and whether"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariba","text_ar":"شَرِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be used to denote this, as it is in the K, requires consideration: (MF:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ra$afahu","text_ar":"رَشَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r$f","text_ar":"رشف"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tara$~afahu","text_ar":"تَرَشَّفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ra$ofN","text_ar":"رَشْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the “ taking ” water “ with the lips; ” and is more than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maS~N","text_ar":"مَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r$f","text_ar":"رشف"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AmtS~hu","text_ar":"امتصّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; (S, M, A, Msb, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tmS~Shu","text_ar":"تمصّصهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, A:) or the last signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did so leisurely."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~um~aAna","text_ar":"الرُّمَّانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AmtS~","text_ar":"امتصّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maS~ahu","text_ar":"مَصَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sucked the pomegranate"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and so of other things. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maS~a AljaAriyapa","text_ar":"مَصَّ الجَارِيَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sucked the damsel's saliva from her mouth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, in L, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mSd","text_ar":"مصد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maS~a mina Ald~unoyaA","text_ar":"مَصَّ مِنَ الدُّنْيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He obtained a little of worldly goods."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["A","Msb","S","M","K","T","TA","MF"]},{"entry_id":"n38624","headword_ar":"مُصَّةٌ","root":"mS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}